## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6fbbc-159">次のコード例のジオメトリック変換をリセットする`pgBrush`id。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fbbc-159">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6fbbc-160">ように仮定`myPath`が既存<xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6fbbc-160">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
PathGradientBrush pgBrush = new PathGradientBrush(myPath);  
 pgBrush.ResetTransform();  
```
